          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " view based on various optional filtering criteria. It allows for the retrieval of billing header information, which includes details such as account numbers, billing periods, amounts due, and other billing-related data. The procedure supports pagination through "
